# WatchIO live parameter updates

**Full playbook:** `.cursor/skills/watchio-live-monitor/SKILL.md` — read before debugging refresh/live freeze.

## Failure signature (quick)

| Log / UI | Likely cause |
|----------|----------------|
| Only `status` + `vartree`, **no** `varleaves`/`add` | Metadata pipeline stuck (was: `varinfo` + no queue timeout) |
| **Description empty** | `serverMetadataLoaded === false` — varleaves never merged |
| Repeated `send list` then updates stop | `type:list` reset stream — use add/delete diff only |
| 1–2s stall then live OK | Awaiting varleaves — use `pinnedMetadata` workspace cache |

## Architecture (do not regress)

| Layer | Responsibility |
|-------|----------------|
| `runPinnedLivePipeline` | **Only** orchestrator for pinned recovery |
| `fetchVarLeaves(branch, true, priority)` | Pinned metadata — **not** `varinfo` on STOMP |
| `syncWatchIoMonitorDiff` | **add/delete only** — never `type:list` on WebSocket |
| `serverMetadataLoaded` | From varleaves or workspace `pinnedMetadata` cache |
| STOMP metadata queue | Serialized varleaves + **3s timeout** |

## Rules

- One pipeline in `useWatchIo` — no parallel monitor-sync effects.
- Defer `selectedBranch` varleaves until pinned metadata ready.
- `isPinnedVariableLiveLoaded` = `serverMetadataLoaded === true`.
- `varlist` → `setSearchVarlistIndex` only (not `mergeVarList`).
- After changes: F5 ×10, description present, log shows `varleaves` → `add` → `update`.
